      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Yves De Billoëz</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/shawn-chidester-62a8b494/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/f/f6/YvesDeBilloez.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:YvesDeBilloez.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Yves De Billoëz <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Yves De Billoëz</b>,<br />\na Belgian <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Information_and_communications_technology\">ICT</a> architect, manager and consultant with expertise in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computer_security\">computer security</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cryptography\">cryptography</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bank\">banking operations</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \nHe is CTO and Co-Founder of <i>eSureCoin.com</i>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Democratic_Republic_of_the_Congo\">Democratic Republic of the Congo</a>, providing banks and financial institutions the ability to offer <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bitcoin\">Bitcoin</a> purchase and sale services <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\nAs avocational computer chess programmer, Yves De Billoëz is author of the <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source engine</a> <a href=\"/Belofte\" title=\"Belofte\">Belofte</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2017_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2017 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Yves_De_Billo%C3%ABz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2017_...\">2017 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Yves_De_Billo%C3%ABz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2017 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=64451\">New engine: belofte</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Yves De Billoëz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 29, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=64512\">Measuring elo rating engine outside tournament</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Yves De Billoëz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 04, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Playing_Strength\" title=\"Playing Strength\">Playing Strength</a> </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=64658\">Configure Arena Linux 1.1 with engines of certain ELO</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Yves De Billoëz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 19, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Arena\" title=\"Arena\">Arena</a>, <a href=\"/Linux\" title=\"Linux\">Linux</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=68153\">Belofte news</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Yves De Billoëz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 07, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72580\">Engine update - belofte 0.9.6 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Yves De Billoëz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 15, 2019</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Yves_De_Billo%C3%ABz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=76817\">C++ code for board[8][8] representation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Yves De Billoëz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 08, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/8x8_Board\" title=\"8x8 Board\">8x8 Board</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=77504\">Hash value composition</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Yves De Billoëz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 17, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Yves_De_Billo%C3%ABz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/yvesdebilloez/\">Yves De Billoëz | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sourceforge.net/projects/belofte/\">Belofte Source code on souceforge</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.quora.com/profile/Yves-De-Billo%C3%ABz\">Yves De Billoëz - Quora</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Yves_De_Billo%C3%ABz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/yvesdebilloez/\">Yves De Billoëz | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.esurecoin.com/about/management-team/\">Who are we – eSureCoin</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\